<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.faitsetcauses.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/Palais-de-justice-de-Montreal_PLD_20110425_157.1000.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-6284" title="Les grandes lignes de la Loi" src="http://www.faitsetcauses.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/Palais-de-justice-de-Montreal_PLD_20110425_157.1000.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="369" /></a></p>
